{
  "id": "RAW_0c920e",
  "title": "进步 or 退化: 记录 Agent 取代我输出的 96 小时",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3MTk3NzYzNw==&mid=2247496332&idx=1&sn=d962b6c9b45263ad72ff4c40f7658832",
  "date": "2025-06-05 10:49:00",
  "author": "AI沃茨",
  "siteName": "卡尔的AI沃茨",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;padding:0px 10px;margin:0px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0em;text-decoration:none;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;font-style:normal;overflow-wrap:break-word;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0em;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-word;background:no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;font-family:PingFangSC-regular, sans-serif;orphans:auto;widows:auto;text-align:left;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这段时间测试的 Agent 真的太多太多了，通用、办公、设计、编程、创作等等等等，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以，完成这一大串任务需要几步人工？</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 BOSS 直聘查找50个AI 领域的程序员岗位，提取信息并生成 Excel 名单。分析这些职位所属公司的重合度，识别最常见的母公司。再提取该公司官网近一年跟AI相关的招聘岗位及描述，导出为 Excel。针对这些岗位，自动写出定制简历，并通过官网投递。</span></strong></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Fellou2.0 这个 Agent 浏览器里，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">答案是1步，复制黏贴</span></strong></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4018566952552726531\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4018566952552726531\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXm5Tr1M91JJZ3N6PHAN1vk0w2Qa13AoTEI3adJunbOp27spnOVjFIP69edibzaRFNaM0AdQ3fna89A%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n   </section>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但测试多了会有一种错觉，我更像个旁观者，而不是创作者。于是当下我的脑海里蹦出一个奇妙的想法，</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 20px 0px;padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px;border-style: none none none solid;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(242, 22, 22, 0.9);border-radius: 0px;background: no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;display: block;overflow: auto;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 是不是在吞噬我的动手能力？当我把所有输出都交由 Agent 完成，本质上是在进步，还是退步？</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以我一拍脑袋，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于 Fellou 2.0 做了四个难度级别等级的测试，来判断我对Agent的依赖风险，聊一聊这场可能影响我未来工作方式的 Agent 热潮，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Here we go！</span></p>\n   <blockquote style=\"margin: 20px 0px;padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px;border-style: none none none solid;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(242, 22, 22, 0.9);border-radius: 0px;background: no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);width: auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;display: block;overflow: auto;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我整理好了所有 Fellou 高阶测试任务清单 + 提示词，公众号回复「Fellou」即可获取。欢迎在评论区分享你最想让 Agent 浏览器完成的任务，我随机抽取跑通工作流提示语</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">&nbsp;01｜</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">先说说 Fellou 是啥？&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fellou，一款Agent 浏览器，说白了就是：</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">我可以发消息让它替我完成所有网页上的事情</span></strong></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\">🔗&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">fellou.ai</span></strong></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">跟一般的 Agent 不一样，它是浏览器的形态，也就说是能保留多个登陆状态，原生支持切换传统搜索和 Agent 式搜索。</span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/100913b0-eafc-4c59-0311-4d9e071b4400/public\" alt=\"布局很简单，左侧搜索、右侧对话\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6240740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0px auto;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 0px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100012671\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/100913b0-eafc-4c59-0311-4d9e071b4400/public\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 0em;text-align: center;font-weight: normal;margin: 5px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">布局很简单，左侧搜索、右侧对话</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">从官方的例子上看，除了基础的3D动画、编程、信息搜索外，它能做一些非常离谱的事。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它可以当客服，将推广信息发送到各个平台，在屏幕前等着用户回复谈价；当甲方找宠物博主们推广猫粮；还可以自己去 Boss 应聘。陆续尝试了 25 个任务后，我开始怀疑人生，甚至 OpenAI 开发布会都没让我转移注意力。。。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">&nbsp;02｜四级难度实测&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fello2 本身是支持并发和多轮对话的，可惜的是没有回放功能，为了展示效果，我将日常零碎的任务们统一成几个大的。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先来一道</span><code style=\"color: rgb(239, 112, 96);font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8em;letter-spacing: 0em;background: no-repeat rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);width: auto;height: auto;margin: 0px 2px;padding: 2px 4px;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">信息收集+文本创作+代码生成</span></code><span leaf=\"\">的混合型任务热热身吧，</span></p>\n   <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"border-radius:5px;display:block;width:764px;margin-bottom:-7px;height:30px;\"></span><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:15px 16px 16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">查找并总结&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;年全球 AI 浏览器市场的主要参与者，结某乎、某书、某博、X等平台讨论 Fellou 这个Agent浏览器，生成分析报告，包含它们的访问量，用户分析等参数，做成可以访问的网页链接，再撰写一篇不少于</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">6</span></span><span leaf=\"\">千字的《浏览器已死，Agent 浏览器已来》的科技文章，发布在 Medium 上。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4018564269053722639\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4018564269053722639\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXm5Tr1M91JJZ3N6PHAN1vk0oWIWEdhibfcW3Oz96Tfv1aVFkgQEaGzIKyLX4o9vibsjCB3UCwpN1rCw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n   </section>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这5个需求完成了4个，这里不得不额外感叹一下，现在 Agent 运行时间越来越长，之后估计分享一个 case 就要录制1小时了。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">还是我来浓缩一下，首先 Fello2 这个思考过程就不太一样，会给不同的 Agent分配不同的步骤，代码生成和文章写作就交给了 code agent，信息收集和发布就给了 browser agent。</span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/00d17d12-16f1-4eeb-d853-b55f7cd35300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0px auto;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 0px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100012669\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/00d17d12-16f1-4eeb-d853-b55f7cd35300/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我很喜欢执行过程中看到不同色块的小框分割网页的内容，以及鼠标移动的轨迹，还有就是超快的打字输入速度。</span></p>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e88fd6e2-849b-4c57-f02c-579a190b4000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6259259259259259\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0px auto;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 0px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100012668\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e88fd6e2-849b-4c57-f02c-579a190b4000/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">来看看生成的网页，</span></p>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4018566502034063372\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4018566502034063372\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXm5Tr1M91JJZ3N6PHAN1vk0miaZEQMWPnIp94sJWE8HibVTfXFKovBcnEty73MicKXmYQVKngbw9Xiciaw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n   </section>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">跟 Deep Research 相比，我会打一个80的质量分，因为交互、信息以及图表都做的挺好的。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">再来说说体验的部分缺点，</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 25px;margin:8px 0px;list-style-type:disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:15px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">有些页面需要登陆，但现在应该是没有主动通知，也没有等待环节，有时候我登陆后，它就应该去搜索其他平台了。</span>\n     </section></li>\n    <li>\n     <section style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:15px;margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8em;margin-bottom:5px;text-align:left;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">因为网络或者大模型报错后，选择</span><code style=\"background: no-repeat rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);width: auto;margin: 0px 2px;padding: 2px 4px;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-family: &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">重新运行</span></code><span leaf=\"\">是默认所有任务都会重跑一次，所以用的时候按照轻量的2-3需求来问，体验感会更好一些</span>\n     </section></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">文章开头的简历投递案例还有一个离谱的变体，</span></p>\n   <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"border-radius:5px;display:block;width:764px;margin-bottom:-7px;height:30px;\"></span><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:15px 16px 16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 BOSS 直聘上找到最新发布的前端工程师的岗位，结合对应的岗位描述和我上传的简历内容写一段自我介绍，并通过“立即沟通”将自我介绍发送给招聘者。发送</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">10</span></span><span leaf=\"\">次。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4018562932781793285\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4018562932781793285\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXm5Tr1M91JJZ3N6PHAN1vk074HpzzepXNGnHsEP73ensickiaaPp4Cick6kmfEODlWTurT2S2TaMcUNw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n   </section>\n   <figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/426e7d10-9055-4a90-9f5b-873e502af700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6333333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0px auto;max-width: 100%;border-style: none;border-width: 3px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius: 0px;object-fit: fill;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;\" data-imgfileid=\"100012670\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/426e7d10-9055-4a90-9f5b-873e502af700/public\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">是真的真的把信息发出去了，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">前些年吹的一天投递世界500强的牛圆回来了。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当然作为一个Agent浏览器，我会自然将它看齐到通用Agent的高度，理论上可以访问网页，准确完成点击、滑动、填写等操作的话，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">做个设计啥的，应该不难吧。</span></p>\n   <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"border-radius:5px;display:block;width:764px;margin-bottom:-7px;height:30px;\"></span><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:15px 16px 16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">搜索尤溪县的建筑风格、文化和形象，帮我做一个 logo，文字：尤溪县城市文旅，元素包含朱熹的形象，金柑的造型，八山一水一分田的山水风光形象，最好的是一个元素里体现三个意思。元素要少，避免复杂像徽章，背景白色扁平简洁。中文的占比是 2x，英文是 1x，图形是 6x。颜色严格控制在 2 色以内，矢量，扁平，美观，产出 10 个陈幼坚的设计风格，其中一个要有 尤溪县 的文化底蕴和形象在其中，另外一个要有刘伯温故居的 logo 设计风格，再有一个把朱熹的头像融入进去。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4018567714523267093\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4018567714523267093\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXm5Tr1M91JJZ3N6PHAN1vk0FibUDt2faINaSuEHOaAdgk6lZNAv6nPnOs2icNaees5ODSkrwRyY50Dw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n   </section>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至Fellou还能充当 RPA 版人工客服，24小时自动回复的case，遗憾的是我实际并没有对应的使用场景，这里放官方的地址来欣看看：</span></p>\n   <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"border-radius:5px;display:block;width:764px;margin-bottom:-7px;height:30px;\"></span><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:15px 16px 16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">跨境电商监控谈价任务：监控 SalesSmartly，回答用户的问题，引导用户完成下单，当用户询问价格的时候，按价格表给到报价，当用户询问物流时间的时候，根据物流时间表给到预计的配送时间，当用户砍价的时候，不能低于我们的底价，预计低价持续的和用户沟通，用户确认订单后立刻生成一个下单的 csv 表（包含：商品名称 + 商品数量 + 商品的单价）。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4018561815268442133\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4018561815268442133\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXm5Tr1M91JJZ3N6PHAN1vk0nmscbrgguiatfGv95nF2n6YrcOhOlfKar29uXibrT1u3wY670dlMvaHw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n   </section>\n   <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap;overflow-wrap: break-word;border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"border-radius:5px;display:block;width:764px;margin-bottom:-7px;height:30px;\"></span><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:15px 16px 16px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">找到X/ins/YT/抖上分别找到粉丝数量在&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">10</span></span><span leaf=\"\">k+ 的&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height:26px;\"><span leaf=\"\">20</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;个宠物博主，同时私信询问她们是否可以合作推广 A 品牌猫粮。把博主信息整理成网页报告.</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></code></pre>\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4018562414047051783\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4018562414047051783\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FYEhakvKZjXm5Tr1M91JJZ3N6PHAN1vk0RicRP7uBXF6JJdTTib6pOT63Yp8JLb5CgDBXv9PqsB9ENm3w6xkFZemQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></iframe>\n   </section>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">&nbsp;03｜“我”还在思考吗？&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fellou，也可以代指 Agent 们，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在它们高度聚合的工作流，以及超长的思考过程里，我开始选择性忽视中间的过程。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d0a57658-85e4-46b4-bbf9-d472557fd500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7518518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100012683\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d0a57658-85e4-46b4-bbf9-d472557fd500/public\">\n   </section>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我开始有点慌。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">因为我已经想不起“我是怎么完成这些事的”，甚至要再现同样的结果的时候，需要先去找当时历史记录的提示语，哪怕只是简单的几句话。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前写稿要翻文献、做卡片笔记、串联关键词。现在？Agent帮我检索、判断正确与否、输出结论。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\">路径感，消失了。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;background:no-repeat rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-style:none;height:auto;\">等于把我的“学习过程”给隐性删除了。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这，值得吗？</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我意识到，自己进入了“Agent 依赖态”，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">所以这篇文章成型前，我给自己留了一天，把AI们关掉，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">重新回到3年前的原始搜索，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果就是，写稿前没有自动梳理的信息源，一篇篇看重复的信息，像在深不见底的大海捞一根针一样，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我在做这个搜索的过程中努力的在问自己，我想要什么，哪些信息是重要的，哪些信息是无聊的不需要的，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我在持续思考，反复询问自己，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">像今天的AI一样</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">于是，我重新划分了角色定位：</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我不再手动操作，但我可以定义“我要抵达哪里”。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">省略掉的这部分思考过程，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">到底是进步，还是退化？</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们能不能拥有一个人类 + Agent 的新模式？</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">答案是：能，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但前提是我们还在提问，我们还在思考，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们还知道“为什么”比“是什么”更重要。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:20px;\">&nbsp;写在最后&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fellou 给我的震撼不只是工具层面的，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它逼着我重新审视“创作”这件事。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你拥有一个全天候不抱怨不疲惫、能并行跑20个网页任务的浏览器助手，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">你就会面临一个问题：</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我还在主动参与这个世界吗？</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">还是只是扮演了一个“发布器”的角色？</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我不知道答案是什么，但我愿意尝试一种新的方式：</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我发问，它工作。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">它执行，我判断。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我和 Agent 一起，</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">完成我一个人无法完成的结构化认知。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这，不是让渡能力。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Agent 浏览器，不是替代品，是放大器。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">真正的边界，是你有没有继续思考。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我思，故我在。</span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.06em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: block;color: gray;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">@ 作者 / 卡尔</span></span><span style=\"display: block;color: gray;font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">@ 动手学AI知识库 / learnprompt.pro</span></span></p><figure data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: center;align-items: center;\">\n   </figure>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "评测 Agent 浏览器 Fellou 自动化能力，探讨 AI Agent 对人类工作方式和思考能力的潜在影响。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "评测 Agent 浏览器 Fellou 自动化能力，探讨 AI Agent 对人类工作方式和思考能力的潜在影响。",
  "summary": "文章深入评测了 Agent 浏览器 Fellou 2.0 的功能和潜力，通过多种任务示例（如信息收集、文本创作、代码生成、简历投递、设计辅助等）展示了其自动化执行网页操作的强大能力。作者探讨了过度依赖 Agent 可能导致的“路径感”缺失和思考能力退化的问题，引发了关于 AI 是否正在“吞噬”人类动手能力的思考。文章最终提出一种人与 Agent 协作的新模式：人负责提问和判断，Agent 负责执行，将 Agent 视为“放大器”而非替代品，强调保持独立思考的重要性，以应对 Agent 技术浪潮对未来工作方式的影响。",
